{"word":"ἐπιθυμητής","slug":"ἐπιθυμητής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιθυμητής</b></el> <el>(ἐπιθῡμητής, οῦ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἐπιθυμέω'><el>ἐπιθυμέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>one who longs for</i> or <i>desires</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>a lover</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}